<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>

  <title>Área Restrita</title>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #333;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #dc3545;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #6c757d;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    a.button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #1f9298;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    a.button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h3 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      a.button {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        padding: 10px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>Acesso Restrito</h1>
  <h3>Efetue login para continuar e acessar esta página.</h3>
  <a href="/login-pac" class="button">Ir para Login</a>
</body>
</html>
